item.title: Hello World
item.description: My First Paragraph Ayy, this is the start of the blog. It already feels like I’m doing an assignment for school. RIP me. This post will mostly discuss the future of these blogs as well as some retrospection as to why I want to do this in the first place. Not really expecting anyone to read this part. I’m honestly using it as an example post so I can style the site properly.
